#RGB각 채널 분류 (1)
title=['Red','Green','Brue']
plt.figure(figsize=(8,4))
for i in range(1,4):
    plt.subplot(1,3,i)
    plt.title(title[i-1])
    plt.imshow(img[200:400,200:400,i-1],cmap='gray')

#RGB각 채널 분류 (2)
plt.figure(figsize=(8,4))
title=['Red','Green','Brue']
RGB=[[1,0,0],[0,1,0],[0,0,1]]
for i in range(1,4):
    plt.subplot(1,3,i)
    plt.title(title[i-1])
    img_1=img*RGB[i-1]
    plt.imshow(img_1,cmap='gray')
